At the second Infecticon base Blight simply smirks as the water beneath 
Alecto and the other people there swirls violently, soon the base is revelaed 
as the ocean swirls around an opening signaling them to enter. Blight then 
turns to Darkfate.

Blight: "Well now... will you agree to my terms or will these bots most 
liekly end up like that shuttle. Which will be destroyed soon enough unless 
you agree, Predacon.."

Elsewhere at the Oblivion, Frostbite smiles as she recieves Zardus's reply.

Frostbite: "My ship would be adequate, I can arrange transportation, or would 
your base be more preferable? Or do you have some other place in mind?"

--part1_123.17411ca.287d1c1b_boundary
